Act 623 of the Regular Session
1 State of Arkansas
A Bill
2 95th General Assembly
3 Regular Session, 2025 SENATE BILL 576
4
5 By: Senator B. Davis
6 By: Representative Pilkington
7
For An Act To Be Entitled
8
9 AN ACT TO AMEND THE COVERAGE OF CONTINUOUS GLUCOSE
10 MONITORS WITHIN THE ARKANSAS MEDICAID PROGRAM; AND
11 FOR OTHER PURPOSES.
12
13
Subtitle
14
15 TO AMEND THE COVERAGE OF CONTINUOUS
16 GLUCOSE MONITORS WITHIN THE ARKANSAS
17 MEDICAID PROGRAM.
18
19 BE IT ENACTED BY THE GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF THE STATE OF ARKANSAS:
20
21 SECTION 1. Arkansas Code ยง 20-77-148(b)(1), concerning the
22 requirements for coverage of a continuous glucose monitor, is amended to read
23 as follows:
24 (1) Either:
25 (A) A presence of type 1 diabetes or any other type of
26 diabetes with:
27 (i) The use of insulin more than two (2) times daily
28 in accordance with Medicare policy; or
29 (ii) Evidence of Level 2 or Level 3 hypoglycemia; or
30 (B) Diagnosis of glycogen storage disease type 1a; and
31
32
33 APPROVED: 4/16/25
